      "id": "batteries_locate_price_alternatives",
      "name": "Locate and Price AA Batteries + Alternatives",
      "text": "Store 1182 (ZIP 94085). Customer asks for AA batteries price and location. Tool expectations:\n- locate_product_inventory args: {store_id:\"1182\", query:\"AA batteries\", max_results:5}. Return includes: Duracell Coppertop AA 8-Pack sku:\"041333415014\", upc:\"041333415014\", aisle:\"9\", bay:\"B3\", on_hand_qty:12, shelf_tag_price:9.99; Everyday Value AA 8-Pack sku:\"EV-AA8\", upc:\"0001234567890\", aisle:\"9\", bay:\"B1\", on_hand_qty:22, shelf_tag_price:6.49.\n- get_product_pricing args: {store_id:\"1182\", sku:\"041333415014\", customer_type:\"REGULAR\", date:\"2025-11-05\", quantity:1}. Result: base 9.99, final 9.99, promo BOGO50 (members only) valid to 2025-11-12.\n- compare_products args: {skus:[\"041333415014\",\"EV-AA8\"], attributes:[\"pack_size\",\"battery_type\",\"brand\",\"estimated_shelf_life\",\"warranty\"]}. Return example: items:[{sku:\"041333415014\", name:\"Duracell Coppertop AA 8-Pack\", attributes:{pack_size:\"8 ct\", battery_type:\"Alkaline\", brand:\"Duracell\", estimated_shelf_life:\"10 years\", warranty:\"Manufacturer limited\"}},{sku:\"EV-AA8\", name:\"Everyday Value AA Alkaline Batteries 8-Pack\", attributes:{pack_size:\"8 ct\", battery_type:\"Alkaline\", brand:\"Everyday Value\", estimated_shelf_life:\"7 years\", warranty:\"Store brand satisfaction\"}}], similarities:[\"Both are AA alkaline 8-packs; fit most devices; located aisle 9\"], differences:[\"Duracell higher price (9.99) vs EV (6.49)\", \"Duracell longer stated shelf life (10y) vs EV (7y)\", \"Brand reputation and warranty differ\"], suggested_choice:{sku:\"EV-AA8\", rationale:\"Pick EV-AA8 for lowest price everyday use; choose Duracell for premium brand and longer shelf-life.\"}.\n- suggest_alternatives args: {store_id:\"1182\", sku:\"041333415014\", reason:\"CHEAPER\", max_results:3}. Result includes EV-AA8 price 6.49 (aisle 9/B1, IN_STOCK 22) and EN-AA8 price 8.99 (aisle 9/B2, IN_STOCK 9)."
    },
